net.wequick.small

Class Bundle

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.wequick.small.Bundle

  • public class Bundle
extends java.lang.Object
    This class consists exclusively of methods that operate on apk plugin.

    All the bundles are loaded by bundle.json. The bundle.json format and usage are in UI Route.

    Each bundle is resolved by BundleLauncher.

    If the pkg is specified in bundle.json, the bundle is refer to a plugin file with file name in converter "lib" + pkg.replaceAll("\\.", "_") + ".so" and resolved by a SoBundleLauncher.

    See Also:
    BundleLauncher
